    base:desc "Model traceability through originating links; use of white‑box analytical friction models (Coulomb‑viscous, Stribeck, Dahl, LuGre) in conjunction with black‑box data‐driven models; comparison between measured and simulated torque signals to validate model accuracy; uncertainties managed via continuous identification."
]

instance dt_technical_connection : DTDFVocab:TechnicalConnection [
    base:desc "Sensor data published through MQTT messages from the robot’s embedded system to the twin’s data ingestion endpoint; one‑way communication, no return traffic."
]

instance standardization : DTDFVocab:Standardization [
    base:desc "Compliance with SysML for structural modelling, UML for reference model, and Asset Administration Shell for asset description; use of MQTT as a standard industrial messaging protocol."
]
